  "title": "ISic001363. Epitaph for Oursoulos",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">Ἐνθάδε</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"κεῖται\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κεῖται</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Οὔρ\n                    σουλος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Οὔρ\n                    σουλος\"><span data-text=\"Οὔρ\n                    σουλος\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Οὔρσουλος\">Οὔρ-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>σουλος</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"ζή\n                    σας\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ζή-<br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[σα]ς</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span> #interpunct <span data-text=\"κη\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κη\">κη</span>´ <span data-text=\"μῆ\n                    νας\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">μῆ-<br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[νας]</span>  <span data-text=\"ς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ς\">ς</span>´ #interpunct <span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ἡμέρ(ας)</span> #stop <span data-text=\"η\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"η\">η</span>´ #interpunct <span data-text=\"τελ\n                    ευτᾷ\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">τελ-<br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>[ευτᾷ]</span>  <span data-text=\"καλανδαῖς\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"Kalendae\">καλ(ανδαῖς)</span>  <span data-text=\"Αὐγούσταις\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"Augustus\">Αὐγ(ούσταις)</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">Ἐνθάδε</span>  <span data-text=\"κεῖται\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κεῖται</span>  <span data-text=\"Οὔρσουλος\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Οὔρσουλος\">Οὔρσουλος</span>  <span data-text=\"ζήσας\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ζήσας</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"κη\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κη\">κη</span>  <span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">μῆνας</span>  <span data-text=\"ς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ς\">ς</span>  <span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ἡμέρας</span>  <span data-text=\"η\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"η\">η</span>  <span data-text=\"τελευτᾷ\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">τελευτᾷ</span>  <span data-text=\"καλανδαῖς\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"Kalendae\">καλανδαῖς</span>  <span data-text=\"Αὐγούσταις\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"Augustus\">Αὐγούσταις</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"κεῖται\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΕΙΤΑΙ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Οὔρ\n                    σουλος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Οὔρ\n                    σουλος\"><span data-text=\"Οὔρ\n                    σουλος\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Οὔρσουλος\">ΟΥΡ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΣΟΥΛΟΣ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"ζή\n                    σας\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΖΗ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[..]Σ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span>()<span data-text=\"κη\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κη\">ΚΗ</span><span data-text=\"μῆ\n                    νας\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[...]</span><span data-text=\"ς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ς\">Σ</span>()<span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡ</span>()<span data-text=\"η\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"η\">Η</span>()<span data-text=\"τελ\n                    ευτᾷ\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">ΤΕΛ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>[......]</span><span data-text=\"καλανδαῖς\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"Kalendae\">ΚΑΛ</span><span data-text=\"Αὐγούσταις\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"Augustus\">ΑΥΓ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"κεῖται\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΕΙΤΑΙ</span><span data-text=\"Οὔρσουλος\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Οὔρσουλος\">ΟΥΡΣΟΥΛΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"ζήσας\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΖΗΣΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"κη\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κη\">ΚΗ</span><span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"ς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ς\">Σ</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"η\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"η\">Η</span><span data-text=\"τελευτᾷ\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">ΤΕΛΕΥΤΑ</span><span data-text=\"καλανδαῖς\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"Kalendae\">ΚΑΛΑΝΔΑΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Αὐγούσταις\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"Augustus\">ΑΥΓΟΥΣΤΑΙΣ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001363_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001363_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001363.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001363-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based on photograph</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"lines 2-3\">lines.2-3: <span>Kirchhoff: Οὐρσοῦλος; Kaibel, Wessel, Korhonen: Οὔρ|σουλος</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"line 4\">line.4: <span>Amico, Kirchhoff, Kaibel, Wessel: κε; Torremuzza, Ferrara, Korhonen: κη</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"lines 5-6\">lines.5-6: <span>Ferrara: τελ[εύτατος] (sic); Kirchhoff: τελ[ευτᾷ---]; Kaibel: τελ(ευτήσας); Korhonen: τελ|[ευτᾷ]</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"line 6\">line.6: <span>Kirchhoff: καλ(ανδ---) Αὐγ[ούστ---]; Kaibel: [τῇ πρὸ ---] καλ(ανδῶν) Αὐγ(ούστων); Wessel: [πρὸ ---] καλ. Αὐγ.; Korhonen: καλ(ανδαῖς) Αὐγ(ούσταις). [τῇ πρ(ὸ) ---] καλ(ανδῶν) Αὐγ(ούστων) seems less probable because of the space left, considering that the verb τελευτάω is never abbreviated in inscriptions from Catania</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>Here lies Oursoulos, having lived for 28 years, 6 months and 8 days. He died on the Kalends of August.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>Qui giace Oursoulos, che ha vissuto per 28 anni, 6 mesi e 8 giorni. È morto nelle Calende di agosto.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>This inscription presents the traditional structure of the Christian funerary inscriptions from Catania, with the formula <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἐνθάδε κεῖται ὁ δεῖνα</span>, the age of the deceased with the participle of <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ζάω</span> and a second sentence introduced by <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">τελευτᾷ</span> (which never appears in the participle form: for this reason, the restoration of Kaibel, <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">τελευτήσας</span>, has to be rejected) with the date of death, <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">dies natalis</span> for the Christians. The name of the deceased, <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Οὔρσουλος</span>, recurs in other inscriptions from the imperial age (IGB 3.1772).</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 1374 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</a>  </li><li> Amico 1741 272 no.18 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1769 188 no.134 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1784 199 no.156 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</a>  </li><li> Ferrara 1829 354 no.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005</a>  </li><li> Kirchhoff 1877 9483 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">544</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 202 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Irregular letters: angular Ε, lunate Σ, cursive Ω. A with a slanted bar (except at l. 1 where the bar is straight), Υ with the form of the Latin V. Interpuncts divide numerals from words.</p> Lines 1-6  20-35  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
