    {
      "id": "commentary",
      "html": "<h2>commentary</h2>  <p>This inscription presents the traditional structure of the Christian funerary inscriptions from Catania, with the formula <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἐνθάδε κεῖται ὁ δεῖνα</span>, the age of the deceased with the participle of <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ζάω</span> and a second sentence introduced by <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">τελευτᾷ</span> (which never appears in the participle form: for this reason, the restoration of Kaibel, <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">τελευτήσας</span>, has to be rejected) with the date of death, <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">dies natalis</span> for the Christians. The name of the deceased, <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Οὔρσουλος</span>, recurs in other inscriptions from the imperial age (IGB 3.1772).</p>  "
    },
    {
      "id": "bibliography",
      "html": "<h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 1374 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</a>  </li><li> Amico 1741 272 no.18 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1769 188 no.134 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1784 199 no.156 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</a>  </li><li> Ferrara 1829 354 no.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005</a>  </li><li> Kirchhoff 1877 9483 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">544</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 202 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  "
    },
